---
title: Chargrilled Capsicum-Stuffed Mushrooms with Caramelised Onion & Roast Potatoes
description: Big portabello mushrooms are the perfect vehicle for a golden, crunchy and cheesy stuffing, which gets baked in the oven for a
delightful main event. Served with a colourful garden salad, this is the most delicious way to get your greens!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
